The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks in feedback control systems to improve trajectory tracking, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, specifically deep neural networks, which could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computer vision (cs.CV).
